    <item>
      <title>特朗普对习近平施加压力，最新威胁要提高关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布了对中国进口的额外关税，这增加了北京进一步报复的风险，以及世界上两个最大经济体之间紧张局势的螺旋螺旋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着加密货币的恶化，比特币从历史高25％下降了25％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/bitcoin-down-25-from-all-time-high-as-crypto-selloff-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周五的亚洲交易时间里，比特币的溃败恶化，使加密货币从不到六周前的历史最高水平下降了四分之一以上，因为交易者在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普当选之后大幅扭转了赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/bitcoin-down-25-from-all-time-high-as-crypto-selloff-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本打击JGB支持贷款的蓬勃发展市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/japan-to-crack-down-on-booming-market-for-jgb-backed-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的金融监管机构计划对670亿美元的高收益贷款进行全面的镇压，这些贷款得到了政府债券和其他资产的支持，即使官员警告他们的风险，这些贷款也在地区银行中广受欢迎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/japan-to-crack-down-on-booming-market-for-jgb-backed-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>机油头每月损失，因为新的关税风险伤害了情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对主要贸易伙伴的关税威胁升级，损害了风险资产的需求，增加美元，并蒙蔽了能源需求的前景，因此OIL每月损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 23:25:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税刺激风险抛售：市场包裹，股票下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税公告促使投资者降低风险赌注之后，全球股票的抛售扩展到亚洲，而美元加强和国库的收益却降低了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 22:35:22 GMT</pubDate>
